To get you started, I've provided some relevant code snippets to the issue:
{{elements_saved_text}}
Moreover, I've created a replication script that replicates the issue:
{{replication_script}}
Running the script, I get the following output:
{{replication_output}}
If you want to run the replication script yourself after making edits, use the run_test tool; it will print SUCCESS if you have fixed the issue, otherwise it will raise an exception.
Remember to wrap your tool calls within {{tools_start}} and {{tools_end}} XML tags.

